headline: From Santa Roosters to Ride-On Mowers, Tractor Supply Gears up for the Holidays Out Here
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., November 18, 2024--Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), the largest rural lifestyle retailer in the United States, has released a first look at upcoming sales, limited-time deals and gift ideas for the holiday season.
